OL,3,CSoaring costs for dairy farmers as
OL,4,Cthey get less for their milk
OL,6,FA Somerset dairy farmer says a drop in
OL,7,Fthe market value of milk will leave
OL,8,Fhim #20,000 a month worse off.
OL,10,FMark Humphry, who has a herd of 400
OL,11,Fcows, says an increase in the amount
OL,12,Fof milk produced across the UK,
OL,13,Fcombined with global demand falling,
OL,14,Fis making it harder to make ends meet.
OL,16,FOver the last five years there has
OL,17,Fbeen a 16 per cent drop in the number
OL,18,Fof dairy farms across the UK, dropping
OL,19,Fto just over 7,000 from almost 8.400
OL,20,Fin 2020.
