OL,3,CSoaring costs for dairy farmers as
OL,4,Cthey get less for their milk
OL,6,FMark, who runs Southey Farm near
OL,7,FTaunton, says he is facing a
OL,8,Fconsiderable shortfall, and little
OL,9,Fprospect of being able to start paying
OL,10,Foff a recent substantial investment in
OL,11,Ftwo new milking parlours.
OL,13,FMark, the fourth generation of his
OL,14,Ffamily to run the farm and the NFU
OL,15,FChair for Somerset, said: "We have
OL,16,Fseen most of our major processors drop
OL,17,Ftheir prices from November so we will
OL,18,Fmake a loss over the winter. So we are
OL,19,Fdropping 5p (a litre) for November and
OL,20,Fthat will impact us by about #20,000 a
OL,21,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
