OL,3,CSoaring costs for dairy farmers as
OL,4,Cthey get less for their milk
OL,6,F"I think it will be a tough year but
OL,7,Ffarmers are resilient and we will get
OL,8,Fthrough the winter."
OL,10,FThis year has seen a huge increase in
OL,11,Fproductivity from the UK dairy
OL,12,Findustry, partly caused by the more
OL,13,Fconcentrated feed given to cows in the
OL,14,Fsummer when the dry weather stopped
OL,15,Fpasture from growing.
OL,17,FThe MP for Glastonbury and Somerton
OL,18,FSarah Dyke - who hails from farming
OL,19,Fstock herself - has just brought a
OL,20,Fbill before parliament, calling for
OL,21,Ffairer milk prices.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
