OL,3,CSoaring costs for dairy farmers as
OL,4,Cthey get less for their milk
OL,6,FShe said: "This price drop is on top
OL,7,Fof so many pressures that farmers are
OL,8,Ffacing already, whether that is the
OL,9,FBrexit trade deals that are ongoing or
OL,10,Findeed the threat of the inheritance
OL,11,Ftax changes."
OL,13,FThe processor Mark supplies - Wyke
OL,14,FFarms in Bruton - says ''Poor trade
OL,15,Fdeals, Inheritance Tax changes and
OL,16,FNational Insurance rises have all
OL,17,Fimpacted our sector significantly."
